Another challenge

Skeleton bones, and a map.

This is a merge challenge

The bones are puzzle pieces, each player has to put together a skeleton. 

They also have a map that shows which grid squares contain certain bones.

Players arrive at a large sandbox "excavation pit" marked like a grid.

Players don't know which piece is at each x on the map, they could for example accidentally dig up two skulls. Players then decide to rebury it, or maybe give it to annother player.
